  After reading other posts, I think you're probably right Itsastony.  Sounds like dinging 61 doesn't hurt AA exp in FG too bad.  I have the 61 damage shield already.  That will help with exp grinding even if I still use the 57 earth in FG.  All those other 61 spells are calling me hard!  lol.<br>
<br>
  I'm definitely staying 61 for a while though and working on AA.  The move to 62 looks like it would really make old world exp tough.  After dinging 61, I may see how exp goes in Akheva.  I suspect if the only place to solo is the entry corridor or the hall to the right, it may be a bit busy there.  It's not unusual for me to be the only one in FG.  No worries about mobs, trains, etc...  Nice for AA grinding. <br>
