<br>
At level 60, level 45+ is dark blue.<br>
<br>
At level 65, level 55+ is dark blue.<br>
<br>
You gain 5 player levels with PoP, but lose 10 mob levels.  Itsatony, not correct.  I think about 20% of the shrooms in FG turn light blue at 61.  It's not huge, but it's something.  Beyond that... Efreeti camp in Sol B is all light blue, Nearly all of Velks is light blue, nearly the entire first floor of Sebilis is light blue, Nearly the whole entrance in Ankheva is light blue, Most of the Gorangas near the zone in Maidens, The Grey goes from dark blues and light blues to light blues and greens, etc etc etc.<br>
<br>
Consider this, MOST Of this game was designed around the fact a level 60 player was the highest.  Many many mobs were created in the lvl 45-49 range for &quot;exp&quot; zones.  That all turns to crap when you level up in PoP. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Master Eandori Raintree<br>
